    },
    {
      "id": "6a2060a600000000008fe8e0",
      "text": "from [井戸端荘:「一緒にメシ食う」しに来ました]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506791,
      "updated": 1780506792
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20609300000000008fe8de",
      "text": ">[クオリアさん.icon]「我々の文明では、[性欲] = [情報共有欲]です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506771,
      "updated": 1780506868
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20609300000000008fe8df",
